title: Mother in Law, apartment
posting_body: I am completing construction on what will soon be a brand new apartment / MIL in a farmhouse in Fall City.
The main part of the house is occupied
but this is a lovely basement apartment with fireplace, full bath, 2 bedrooms, kitchen.
There is good light from windows and very spacious.
It is on 1.5 acres that is shared with the occupants of the main floor.
Ideal tenant will want to participate in what the yard and property offers.
Walking distance to downtown Fall City.
This is a rare opportunity and will not last long so even though it is not finished yet I hope to provide advance notice to find the perfect tenant.
